	abstract = {Ma HI, Trombly CA, Wagenaar RC, Tickle-Degnen L: Effect of one single auditory cue on movement kinematics in patients with Parkinson‚Äôs disease. Am J Phys Med Rehabil 2004;83:530‚Äì536.
        Objective:¬†
